      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a museum-grade E92 M3 featuring the legendary S65 naturally aspirated V8. This specimen is mechanically flawless; rod bearings have been preventatively addressed with BE Bearings and ARP bolts to ensure bottom-end longevity. The M-DCT dual-clutch transmission executes lightning-fast shifts with zero hesitation or clutch slippage. Recent Blackstone Labs oil analysis confirms nominal wear metals, and the subframe has been borescope-inspected for total structural integrity. Finished with a multi-stage paint correction and ceramic coating, this is a turn-key, collector-quality machine for the discerning driver who demands peak atmospheric performance.",
